        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer435614296" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2267449444806305297">Danielle Sibarium has done it again. She has written a young adult novel that is spellbinding. We start with a premonition from our female lead, Jenna Kingsley has ‘feelings’ about the future from touching any object belonging to a person. She touches the ring of Reese Walton and knows that he will break her heart. As the relationship develops Sibarium successfully leads us on a roller coaster of emotions. Jenna’s past collides with Reese’s troubles and we are unable to put the book down. It hoo</span>
  <span id="freeText2267449444806305297" style="display:none">Danielle Sibarium has done it again. She has written a young adult novel that is spellbinding. We start with a premonition from our female lead, Jenna Kingsley has ‘feelings’ about the future from touching any object belonging to a person. She touches the ring of Reese Walton and knows that he will break her heart. As the relationship develops Sibarium successfully leads us on a roller coaster of emotions. Jenna’s past collides with Reese’s troubles and we are unable to put the book down. It hooks us. The end is both surprising and unsettling, leaving us hungry for the sequel.<br /><br />This author has taken a popular forum, young adult romance, and transformed it. She has made it her own. With masterful skill she weaves her tale with believable dialog and action. This is the difference between technical skill and talent. This author has talent. While this is a popular genre, Sibarium adds her magic and it rises from the ordinary to the classic. She takes the genre and it becomes unique because she makes it her own. I look forward with great anticipation to the sequel and remain baited, hooked, and caught by this powerful talent.<br /><br /> <br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="2267449444806305297" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


