<span id="freeTextContainer9346337540726061043">I think this would be a great book for young adults and those experiencing first love, like the main character of the story Jenna.I was hoping for more of the supernatural as Jenna has the gift of touching people and knowing a bit about them or the future. Maybe book two will have more of this. I didn&apos;t realize this was a series when I first got the book. Despite the cover, I didn&apos;t think this book would be more of a romance story than anything else, so for me it wasn&apos;t the type of book I usuall</span>
  <span id="freeText9346337540726061043" style="display:none">I think this would be a great book for young adults and those experiencing first love, like the main character of the story Jenna.I was hoping for more of the supernatural as Jenna has the gift of touching people and knowing a bit about them or the future. Maybe book two will have more of this. I didn't realize this was a series when I first got the book. Despite the cover, I didn't think this book would be more of a romance story than anything else, so for me it wasn't the type of book I usually read but for fans of romance, I think this book would be great, that's why it is getting four stars. If you like young love with a slight twist, this is definitely a book for you.</span>
